<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<android.support.design.widget.CoordinatorLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:descendantFocusability="blocksDescendants"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="@color/android_red_dark">

    <android.support.design.widget.AppBarLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:theme="@style/ThemeOverlay.AppCompat.Dark.ActionBar"/>

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/helptext"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_marginTop="50dp"
        android:textSize="40dp"
        android:textColor="#fcfcfc"
        android:text=""/>

    <ScrollView
        android:id="@+id/listview"
        android:layout_width="fill_parent"
        android:layout_height="fill_parent"
        android:layout_marginTop="@dimen/fragment_tabs_margin_top"
        android:background="#fcfcfc"
        android:gravity="center"
        android:horizontalSpacing="4dp"
        android:divider="#fcfcfc"
        android:padding="4dp"
        android:scrollbars="none"
        android:stretchMode="columnWidth"
        android:verticalSpacing="4dp"
        android:layout_below="@+id/tb_help">

        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:paddingTop="30dp"
            android:gravity="center_horizontal"
            android:paddingLeft="24dp"
            android:paddingRight="24dp">

        <TextView
            android:id="@+id/textView1"
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
            android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
            android:minLines="2"
            android:text="RULES / GUIDELINES: \n\n

- The boundaries are Amul, Reddy's, Nandini and the Post Office, beyond which there are no locations. All clues point to locations within these corners.\n\n

- Once the team of 3 or 4 arrives at the SAC, they will be given their story from the organizers there.\n\n

- On the first sheet that they get, there will be an introduction/prologue to the story along with 5 clues, which will point to a location in the campus. \n\n

- On solving the clue and reaching the required destination in any order whatsoever, they will be asked to perform a particular task at the location.\n\n

- Successfully performing the given task gives the team the next segment of the story. \n\n

- Deciphering all the 5 clues successfully and hence, obtaining the whole story along with all its parts, the team has to solve the mystery and accordingly write the answer in their given sheet and submit it to the people at the SAC.\n\n"
            android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceMedium"
            android:textColor="#81100B" />
        </LinearLayout>

    </ScrollView>

</android.support.design.widget.CoordinatorLayout>
